Hey, did Ramulus get carried to a CR chamber, or is he still in stasis lock 
at the battle scene?

::Prowl::

Prowl nods, running over to an equipment crate and retrieving the devices 
Iron Raptor wanted. He runs back to her, handing her the tube and knife.

"Anything else?" he asks, looking at Dinobot.
